### 1) Health check — should return status UP
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Accept: application/json


### 2) Welcome with no name — should default to "Customer"
GET http://localhost:8080/api/welcome
Accept: application/json


### 3) Welcome with name — should greet by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/welcome?name=Chinmay
Accept: application/json
